name: ROSEMARY
description:
An 18 page book filled with photographs by myself that capture the character of my Grandad and his emotions as he comes to change in the recent death of my Nan. A personal tale that expresses sorrow, looniness and humour. 

This is only a small part of the capture of my Grandad as the progression of this documentation will continue as long is it can.
